This story starts at Twilights castle.\.\.\. Recently Twilight faced yet another change in her life. After years, one of her dearest friends, Sunset Shimmer, finally came back to Equestria again.

Why you might ask?\.\.\. Well in the human world \.\.(and I mean completely human, \.\.because\.\. you know.\| 'Anthros' and stuff in here)\.\.\. her powers werent needed anymore. \.\.The girls experienced enough challenges together to learn how to use their powers correctly. This worlds Twilight was finally ready to lead the group on her own, giving Sunset the chance to go back home.

Which brings us back to the very moment.\.\.\. It is a beautiful, sunny and very hot summer day in equestria. Everything's peaceful and quiet. \.\.\.However, the heroines  of our story are already preparing their next adventure at Twilight's castle. And here begins our story. I will tell you the story about a group of girls that...
Girls come quick! You have to see this!
Yeah, or you just interrupt me and do it yourself.
Calm down Twilight! \.\.You already sound like Rainbow Dash. *chuckle*
I know, I know. But Im just so excited! Look at this!

Indeed, there was something special today. \.\.\.The cutie map, which already sent Twilight and her friends to several places in and beyond Equestria to solve friendship problems, was now glowing with several cutiemarks.
Why does the map call four of us. Thats unusual.\.\.\. I mean, that is too big for a simple 'friendship problem', isn't it?
Yeah, and apparently it only sends unicorns.
Looking at your abilities we should rather say an alicorn and TWO unicorns. *chuckle*
Well, Im just glad I dont have to do this alone. I wouldn t have been able to do such a mission on my own.
But Starlight is right. \.\.Its odd that the map sends my best students and me on a mission.\.\.\. Looks like this might be a tough one.
Trixie, Im sure she didnt mean you by that.
This is quite far away. Is it even still part of Equestria?
Looks like its at the very border of the country. Look, theres still a train leading to it.
These small things look like some old ruins...
Mmh, I think Ive seen these before in a book thats somewhere in the library.
No we sadly have no time for that. This is why I invited you over, Rarity. \.\.Im sorry to ruin your vacation days with that burden, but I need somepony to look up for more infos about that place.
Dont worry, darling. Im always happy to help my friends. I will take care of everything while you are gone.
Thank you! \|Then we can start our journey.\.\.\. But first we should buy some supplies from town.
.\.\..\.\..\.\.\. *sigh* And where do I start now?
A fallen tree is blocking the path! We cant go there!
We could simply climb over the trunk.
Trust me, Sunset. Its better we dont!
How often do I have to say that thats not Applejack?
Lets turn around. After the storm last night shes probably occupied with her animals anyways.
I dont think we have time for that.
